             was indicted for <rs id="t18160710-21-off89" type="offenceDescription">
                     <interp inst="t18160710-21-off89" type="offenceCategory" value="violentTheft"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t18160710-21-off89" type="offenceSubcategory" value="highwayRobbery"></interp>
               feloniously assaulting 
                     <persName id="t18160710-21-victim189" type="victimName">
                        Charles 
                        Robertson
                     <interp inst="t18160710-21-victim189" type="surname" value="Robertson"></interp>
