                     <join result="defendantPunishment" targOrder="Y" targets="t18160710-21-defend188 t18160710-21-punish93"></join>
               DEATH
            </rs>, aged 45.</p>

               <p>First Middlesex Jury, before Mr. Justice Abbot.</p>
